patthana16.92:1.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ niyyānikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naniyyāniko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.92:2.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ aniyyānikaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nasanidassanasappaṭigho naaniyyāniko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi …pe… avigate tīṇi.
